title: Neulsome Studio
description: For 7 years, I have had a crush on my friend's girlfriend, but suddenly she became my girlfriend. How is that even possible? Well, it's all thanks to a well-written script that I composed. A good storyline is what immerses the actors. In the drama "Crank In" a drama solely for me, brought to you by the "Neulsom Studio"!
author: Ullkki
